dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Patrick Jackson. May I have your name, please?
Hi Patrick, my name is Madison Scott.
Nice to meet you, Madison. Could you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, it's zero zero two five six.
Thank you, Madison. Could you also confirm your address, including the street number, city, and zip code?
Of course. My address is five four three Cedar Lane, Springfield, zero two one two three.
Thank you for confirming that, Madison. Is there anything specific you'd like to inquire about today regarding your policy or coverage?
I wanted to ask about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
I can assist you with that. Let's discuss the details. Thank you for your time, Madison. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Patrick, for your assistance.
You're welcome, Madison. Have a great day!
